<div class="order-2 flex flex-col justify-end gap-2 sm:order-0 sm:col-start-1">
  <h1 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-wide">DECISIONS</h1>
  <p>
    I structured the user flow around three priorities: present the brand, prioritize shopping, then
    provide resources for deeper engagement. An interactive hero section leads the page, followed by
    the best-selling products to encourage conversions. Site-wide content was rewritten with AI
    assistance to make it concise, clear, and aligned with the original meaning. Brand identity was
    maintained through earthy tones, re-used written material and imagery, and the existing
    Squarespace template. The site layout uses clearly labeled sections with color changes and
    borders for easy scanning, while shop and blog pages were reorganized into scannable grids. The
    mobile layout was fully reworked to accommodate these changes.
  </p>
